============================================================================
This package includes the Database (FA_*.DAT) and a code (FA_OPD.f90)
that reads and uses the database.

All the variables are specifically illustrated at the beginning of the code.
============================================================================
input.txt:
includes: (1). Fractal Dimension
          (2). Monomer Diameter
          (3). Particle Size Type (Single-size/Size distribution)
          (4). Particle Size Unit (Monomer number/Equivalent Volume Diameter)
          (5). Monomer number/D_EFF; SIGMA for Lognormal Distribution
          (6). Wavelength
          (7). Refractive Index 

output.txt:
includes: (1). Extinction and absorption cross section
          (2). Mass Extinction and absorption cross section
          (3). Single Scattering Albedo
          (4). Asymmetry Factor
          (5). Phase Function P11

============================================================================
